@startuml
!theme plain

title Diagramme de sequence - Facturation patient (sortie hospitalisation)

autonumber

actor Secretaire as "Secretaire / Admin clinique"
boundary UI as "Angular / Mobile"
control API as "FacturationPatientController"
control Service as "FacturationPatientService"
control PDF as "FacturePatientPdfService"
database DB as "Base de donnees"

Secretaire -> UI: Selectionner hospitalisation terminee
UI -> API: POST /api/facturation-patient/generer
API -> Service: genererDepuisHospitalisation(request)
Service -> DB: Charger hospitalisation + patient
Service -> Service: Cloturer sejour (date sortie, chambre liberee)
Service -> Service: Calculer jours + lignes prestations CNAM
Service -> DB: Sauver facture (statut BROUILLON)
DB --> Service: FacturePatient
Service --> API: Facture brouillon
API --> UI: Facture creee

Secretaire -> UI: Emettre la facture
UI -> API: POST /api/facturation-patient/{id}/emettre
API -> Service: emettre(id)
Service -> Service: BROUILLON -> EMISE
Service --> API: Facture emise

Secretaire -> UI: Valider paiement ticket moderateur
UI -> API: POST /api/facturation-patient/{id}/valider-paiement
API -> Service: validerPaiement(id, {montantPaye, modePaiement})
Service -> Service: EMISE -> PAYEE
Service --> API: Facture payee

Secretaire -> UI: Teletransmettre CNAM
UI -> API: POST /api/facturation-patient/{id}/teletransmettre
API -> Service: teletransmettre(id)
Service -> Service: Generer ref CNAM + PAYEE -> TELETRANSMIS
Service --> API: TeletransmissionResult
API --> UI: Reference teletransmission

Secretaire -> UI: Telecharger PDF
UI -> API: GET /api/facturation-patient/{id}/pdf
API -> PDF: genererPdf(id)
PDF -> DB: Detail facture + lignes
PDF --> API: bytes PDF
API --> UI: application/pdf

@enduml
